that the actual value is somewhere between 24 cm and 26 cm, approximately. =
In contrast, a reported value of 25.0 cm implies that the actual value is s=
omewhere between 24.9 cm and 25.1 cm, approximately.</p><div id=3D"h.p_ID_3=
